name: 14 Memory Card - Crayola
description: This special series robot released by Kala Corp. is equipped with a super large RAM capacity and high AI which makes it one of the best sellers. In addition to its appearance that can be customized according to the owner's wishes, the Crayola unit which is intended to be a friend for exploration/adventure is equipped with the main feature of being waterproof to the depths of the bathial zone.
